Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be cured of your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to piece together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like some unimaginable\Nchange is about to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that\Nthey misdiagnosed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have a malignant tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you will gradually\Nbecome paralyzed and then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how am I going to be cured?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here to be comforted by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only telling you what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you. Please spare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have to pay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.\NI'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the parking lot at Daikoku wharf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to our futures lies there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some money.\NThat'll settle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to break you to pieces\Nuntil the girls are satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, Akemi.\NThis is some pervert we've got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo?! What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you! What did you do to Akemi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.29,0:22:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo's... Nagumo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo died...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.13,0:24:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I tell ya.\NThis medicine sure stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.30,0:24:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best thing for stings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.31,0:24:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.42,0:24:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is overcoming my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.22,0:25:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.93,0:25:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! That light!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.47,0:25:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.27,0:25:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.82,0:25:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.24,0:25:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.49,0:25:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ultra God!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.54,0:25:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.29,0:25:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.13,0:25:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my fault.\NIt couldn't have been my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.30,0:25:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer... Hurry up and answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.81,0:25:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.27,0:26:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Kuroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.57,0:26:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.69,0:27:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.45,0:27:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no! Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.00,0:27:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.58,0:28:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We're not going to make it! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.50,0:29:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where's the Ultra God?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.87,0:29:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.04,0:29:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a real ghostly air remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.33,0:29:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.05,0:29:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We were too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.10,0:30:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.15,0:30:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you didn't notice sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.61,0:30:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.53,0:30:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, take a look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.36,0:30:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a video camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.78,0:30:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good find.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.78,0:30:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.20,0:30:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a waste of\Ntime coming here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.04,0:30:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.21,0:30:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.93,0:30:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.68,0:30:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.60,0:30:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and we received a\Ncall from the police earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.44,0:30:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have found your motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.03,0:30:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you walked home last night,\NI filed a report for a stolen bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.21,0:31:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why isn't there anything\Nabout yesterday in the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.63,0:31:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know for sure that Nagumo was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.97,0:31:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't they found him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.76,0:31:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.35,0:31:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember.\NHow exactly did I get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.48,0:31:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that supposed to\Nbe a dream or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.66,0:31:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yuri? What on earth happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.16,0:31:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not showing up at school like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.28,0:31:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.87,0:31:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri? What's the matter, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.89,0:32:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.18,0:32:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.94,0:32:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.48,0:32:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo? Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.65,0:32:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, somehow I ended\Nup at Red Brick Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.65,0:32:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Brick Park? What are you\Ndoing there so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.24,0:32:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to get a hold of you\Nsince last night. Yuri's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.04,0:32:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yuri is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.62,0:32:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.63,0:32:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.63,0:32:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I don't know\Nwhat the hell is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.22,0:32:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo shows up at school\Nlike nothing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.22,0:32:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and not a scratch on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.85,0:32:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.82,0:33:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.78,0:33:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.66,0:33:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell whoever it is I'm not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.41,0:33:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.71,0:33:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.88,0:33:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.59,0:33:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.38,0:33:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.84,0:33:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.84,0:33:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to\Nsay at times like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.26,0:33:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.22,0:33:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were\Ngoing to tell him straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.52,0:33:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.35,0:33:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would he have done that to Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.98,0:33:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I'll tell him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.73,0:33:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you sure? But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.40,0:33:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think a girl can deal with\Nthis sort of thing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.78,0:33:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takamine Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.45,0:33:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.33,0:33:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt strangely compelled\Nto answer Ozaki's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.59,0:34:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Nagumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.26,0:34:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.18,0:34:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better come for\Nyour biopsy this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.22,0:34:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki? Hey, Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.43,0:34:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time had stopped at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.48,0:34:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I realized everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.27,0:34:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why he had called me. And why he's\Nstaking so much on becoming champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.90,0:34:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo? Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.86,0:34:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki might have cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.41,0:34:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.12,0:34:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.08,0:34:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.34,0:34:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Mika didn't know\Nwhat to say to Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.18,0:34:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we just walked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.18,0:34:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.35,0:34:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was moving in a\Ndirection that I hadn't anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.11,0:35:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.95,0:35:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.49,0:35:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, the tumor\Ndidn't show up on the x-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.00,0:35:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did a regular\Ncheck-up just last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.46,0:35:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it's a fault with the MRI.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.54,0:35:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be cured of your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.92,0:35:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel, Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.13,0:35:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.51,0:35:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my memory's been\Nhazy since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.76,0:35:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.81,0:35:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that does happen\Nin the case of brain tumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.02,0:35:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's do a blood test.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.31,0:35:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it, but you may\Nhave been completely cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.07,0:35:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next week we'll do another MRI.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.91,0:35:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could've happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.24,0:35:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I really have been cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.83,0:35:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was what Akemi said really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.80,0:36:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Some kind of amateur porn?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.72,0:36:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.76,0:36:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it kind of exciting to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.39,0:36:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.60,0:36:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Boss! It's him! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.35,0:36:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.53,0:36:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it was\Nworth looking into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.37,0:36:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, how can you just\Nleave that demi-beast alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.45,0:36:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amanojaku is no ordinary demi-beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.54,0:36:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.54,0:36:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't we be in more trouble\Nif he gets to the Ultra God first?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.30,0:36:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seigenki...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.89,0:36:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't obey me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.68,0:36:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not going to let you off...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.02,0:36:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just because you're my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.90,0:37:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Suikakuju has fought\Nwith him many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.57,0:37:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he can't seem to ever\Nsettle it once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.95,0:37:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not capable as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.70,0:37:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.20,0:37:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your order is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.87,0:37:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be sure to defeat him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.92,0:37:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.26,0:37:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a report of an unusual\Nincident in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.97,0:37:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an incident last night that I\Nthought I should report to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.85,0:37:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the malignant brain tumor\Nhas disappeared without surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.11,0:37:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not another case of fraud\Nlike in France recently, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.28,0:37:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.36,0:37:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the data I sent you, I've also\Nincluded results of his blood test.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.07,0:38:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His genetic make-up seems to be\Ngetting closer to what we think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.62,0:38:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have it checked out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.54,0:38:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.38,0:38:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.89,0:38:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.14,0:38:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't confirm it with him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.73,0:38:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.99,0:38:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.49,0:38:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one closest to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.24,0:38:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know him better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.20,0:38:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't at all aware of the\Nsuffering he was going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.88,0:38:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.84,0:38:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only thinking about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.38,0:38:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not... That's not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.18,0:39:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?\NWhy does it have to be Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.48,0:39:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I supposed to be cured? Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.88,0:39:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.19,0:39:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.98,0:39:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki's somehow regained\Nhis strength and has gotten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.78,0:39:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he seems to be hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.95,0:40:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Ozaki be eliminated\Nfrom the tournament here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.20,0:40:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homma of Kaisei College\Nhas ample energy left.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.75,0:40:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki has just gotten\Nup but he still looks shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.96,0:40:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can he really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.25,0:40:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.46,0:40:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.98,0:40:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.07,0:40:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Homma?\NYou'll lose points for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.81,0:41:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.85,0:41:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.27,0:41:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the arrangements?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.61,0:41:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokakuryu is on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.69,0:41:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.69,0:41:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.15,0:42:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worse than an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.99,0:42:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I think I wanted\Nit to be you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.04,0:42:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should apologize, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.96,0:42:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't even aware of\Nwhat was going on with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.63,0:42:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed as a manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.01,0:42:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll support you as\Nbest as I can until you're cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.09,0:42:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it'll be the three of us.\NJust like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.64,0:42:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.64,0:42:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's been going\Non with me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.56,0:42:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see things that aren't there and\NI'm haunted by hallucinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.98,0:42:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not sure if what's\Nhappening is real or a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.41,0:42:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.12,0:42:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! Look at the way\Nyou won your fight today!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.79,0:42:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.25,0:42:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I really win?! Tell me how I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.09,0:43:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even remember\Nhow it played out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.97,0:43:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to just forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.10,0:43:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.85,0:43:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't.\NAnd please don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.61,0:43:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.36,0:43:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.78,0:43:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please! Let me be close to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.00,0:43:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.42,0:43:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.69,0:44:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a blackout? That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.11,0:44:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.15,0:44:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.03,0:44:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.66,0:44:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.17,0:44:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.17,0:44:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hallucination?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.71,0:44:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.13,0:44:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.21,0:44:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is reality. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.30,0:44:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm taking your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.85,0:44:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the Ultra God's woman\Nwould be such a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.06,0:44:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.48,0:44:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.48,0:44:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.73,0:44:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ultra God has a Lolita fetish?\NThese tits aren't even fully developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.37,0:44:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.87,0:44:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.66,0:45:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Dokakuryu,\Nwill take care of your woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.17,0:45:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.63,0:45:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like you know a\Nthing or two about this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.10,0:45:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.89,0:45:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to be ravaged\Nin front of the one you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.11,0:45:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You feel better the\Nmore you hear him writhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.28,0:45:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.49,0:45:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better hurry up, Ultra God. Or\Nyour woman will be of no use to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.25,0:45:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ultra God.\NIf you want your woman back...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.13,0:45:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you will have to\Nreveal your true powers!